1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,080
大家早安

2
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:12,800
The four books of the gospel Matthew, Mark, Luke, and John

3
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:18,720
在師父音書中 馬太 馬可 路加 約翰

4
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:26,000
They tell of the life of our Lord Jesus Christ

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,600
他們都講述了耶穌的生平

6
00:00:29,520 --> 00:00:33,840
In essence, the life of our Lord Jesus Christ

7
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:39,200
is the object lesson that teaches us about God

8
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:42,840
其實 耶穌的生平就是一個實質的教導

9
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:44,840
關於神的一生

10
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:48,680
He is the Word who became flesh

11
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:51,680
祂就是道 成了肉身

12
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:54,520
The Word is Jesus

13
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:56,280
而這道就是耶穌

14
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:59,600
and Jesus Himself is the Living Word

15
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:02,840
祂就是那個生命

16
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:08,400
The Word that we preach and read and hear

17
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:12,480
is more than a simple study of literature

18
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:17,200
我們所講 所聽 所讀的聖經裡面的話語

19
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:19,120
不單只是文字

20
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:23,560
It is more than evidence that validates history

21
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:28,040
祂也是一個見證歷史 不單只是一個見證歷史的證據

22
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:32,480
也不是單單是解說神學的一些的證據

23
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:36,960
也不是單單是解說神學的一些的證據

24
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:42,360
The Word demands our attention to God's voice

25
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:46,520
這個道需要我們真的去專心 專注在神的聲音上

26
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:50,400
and therefore it requires us to respond

27
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:55,160
it requires a response from man's heart

28
00:01:55,160 --> 00:02:00,560
而且真的需要我們人從心裡面的去回應

29
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:06,400
The story from the passage we read earlier of the rich young man

30
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:11,840
is found in three of the four Gospel books

31
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:14,040
剛才我們所唸的經文呢

32
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:17,600
在詩福音裡面有三個福音書記載著

33
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,720
Three times

34
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,640
三次

35
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:29,520
We learn that repetition in scripture reinforces the emphasis of its intent meaning

36
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:33,960
我們知道如果有幾次的加重的去疏縮的時候呢

37
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,480
我們就知道它的意義特別的重要

38
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:41,240
Heaven recorded three times by three different writers

39
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:49,040
The story of the rich young man amplifies God's desire for us to examine our motives

40
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:53,080
as believers in these modern times

41
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:56,920
而這個故事呢 真的神也是要在這個世代

42
00:02:56,920 --> 00:03:02,000
特別的去告訴我們這裡面所藏在的意義

43
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:06,760
What does it mean to be a Christian?

44
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:10,360
做一個基督徒有什麼意義呢

45
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:13,360
Who should Christians follow?

46
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:16,160
我們基督徒是跟從誰呢

47
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:19,520
How should Christians live?

48
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:22,440
我們基督徒要如何的去生活

49
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:24,360
What does being a Christian mean?

50
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:26,440
Who should Christians follow?

51
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:29,920
And how should Christians live?

52
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:33,560
我們要如何的去做 如何的去跟隨

53
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:37,680
我們真的知道我們是去聽誰的話語

54
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,600
Let us pray

55
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:41,200
我們低頭禱告

56
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:46,760
Emily, Father, may we experience your presence in our gathering this morning

57
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:50,400
天父 願我們真的感覺到你與我們同在

58
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:55,840
Father, may your spirit arouse ours as we listen to your word

59
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:59,960
願你的靈來激勵我們當我們在聽你的話語的時候

60
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:06,120
And may your love fill this space as we worship the name above all names

61
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:12,280
願你的靈 你的愛充滿這個地方 讓我們真的來一起的送贈你的名

62
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,920
The name of our Lord Jesus Christ

63
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:17,120
也來送贈我們耶穌基督的名

64
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,680
Our Master, our King, and our Savior

65
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:21,480
我們的主 我們的神

66
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,680
And in His name we all pray

67
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,560
我們奉主的名禱告

68
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:29,240
And the church says Amen

69
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:41,120
在這個經文之前 我們就看到耶穌跟一般的孩子在一起

70
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:43,720
祂跟他們一起玩

71
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,920
祂擁抱他們

72
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:51,000
祂也跟他們一起唱歌 一起的歡笑

73
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:56,400
或者祂也跟他們跳舞吧

74
00:04:56,400 --> 00:05:00,160
這時候祂沒有教導他們

75
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,680
也沒有訓話他們

76
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:06,080
也沒有在指責他們

77
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:25,280
而在父母還有一些成人的圍觀之下

78
00:05:25,280 --> 00:05:34,640
耶穌好像就變回了一個小孩一樣

79
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:42,000
我們看到耶穌和孩童之間有一個很特別的關係

80
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:52,280
因為他們之間的互動是非常溫暖的

81
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:58,280
看到他們有這麼的歡樂 好像耶穌在舉行一個假期的聖經學校一般

82
00:05:58,280 --> 00:06:11,680
祂也沒有告訴父母說 你們可以去做你們的事 我來照顧你們的孩子

83
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:15,800
因為耶穌並不是這樣的

84
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:29,040
因為耶穌要教導成人們 他們帶著孩童的眼光去看祂

85
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:42,880
我們真的需要去學習怎樣把我們的孩子介紹給神

86
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:46,840
也讓神來認識他們

87
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,280
第一

88
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:56,840
Keep an open mind and an open heart as you welcome children into the presence of the Lord

89
00:06:56,840 --> 00:07:00,080
當我們把孩子帶到神的同在的時候

90
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:03,920
我們自己本身就有一個開放的思想和心靈

91
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:11,040
你希望耶穌怎麼對待你的孩子呢

92
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:14,920
你希望祂能接受他們

93
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:18,560
你希望祂能夠聆聽他們

94
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:22,160
跟他們有一個同樣的心智

95
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:34,560
耶穌的溫柔慈愛就是我們現在小孩們的需要

96
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,240
第二

97
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:41,960
Give children permission to be who they are

98
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:47,160
so that they may discover the person of the Lord

99
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:50,800
我們要給小孩一個他們適合的環境

100
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:54,920
讓他們與神之間能夠去產生一個彼此的關係

101
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:58,800
耶穌是一個很關懷人

102
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,560
是一個很慈愛的

103
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:04,000
也是一個很饒恕人的

104
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:16,240
所以對我們小孩的身心靈的發展都是很重要的

105
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,760
第三

106
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:24,520
Show grace so that our children may learn and know the promise of our Lord

107
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:26,880
我們真的要把恩典彰顯出來

108
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:30,360
因為讓我們的小孩能夠知道神的應許

109
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:33,480
耶穌擁抱他們

110
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:36,800
把手按在他們的頭上

111
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:39,160
祂祝福他們

112
00:08:39,160 --> 00:08:45,640
我們要記得恩典不只是一次性的

113
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:54,880
我們要把恩典彰顯出來的時候

114
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:57,680
就是要繼續地為我們的孩子禱告

115
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,800
也要去愛他們

116
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:04,800
因為我們知道耶穌從來沒有放棄我們

117
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:11,720
我們也不要放棄我們的孩子

118
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:17,520
然後耶穌轉頭向成人們說

119
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:20,040
讓他們來到我面前

120
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:25,400
不要禁止他們

121
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:33,920
and you must also be like them in order to receive the kingdom of God

122
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:37,200
而且你們自己也要學像孩子一樣

123
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,680
那麼你們才能夠承受神的國

124
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,720
What a sobering lesson

125
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:45,160
所以這是一個很驚醒的學習

126
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:51,360
Something to keep in mind as we evaluate our own children's ministry

127
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:54,280
當我們看我們自己兒童的施工的時候

128
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:57,320
對我們來說也是一個很驚醒的學習

129
00:09:57,320 --> 00:10:00,120
Let's pray that the Lord may give us wisdom

130
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:02,960
願我們禱告我們神能夠賜給我們智慧

131
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:05,960
May God help us not to be a hindrance

132
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,880
讓我們自己本身也不要成為一個阻礙

133
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:14,200
Because you see it's not only the responsibility of the Sunday school teachers

134
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:17,960
而且我們知道這不單只是足了學老師的責任

135
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:21,360
As parents, it's your responsibility as well

136
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,840
做父母這個也是我們的責任

137
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:27,800
We all have a part in our children's ministry

138
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:32,240
我們每一個人在兒童施工裡面都是一份子

139
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:39,560
Whether at church, at home, or at the restaurant

140
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:41,120
就算在餐館裡面

141
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:46,600
Don't forbid your children to come to me, Jesus says

142
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:50,080
耶穌說不要禁止你的孩子來到我的面前

143
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:53,320
You are their parents

144
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:57,480
你是他們的父母

145
00:10:57,480 --> 00:11:01,280
但是他們是神的兒女

146
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:06,080
Now we come to our text this morning, our passage

147
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:09,640
現在我們就來到今天我們剛才讀的經文上

148
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:13,160
A young man ran so fast

149
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:17,560
pushes his way through the crowd and falls before Jesus

150
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:20,240
我們看到這個年輕人跑得很快

151
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:23,120
然後他就來到耶穌面前跪在他的面前

152
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:26,800
Sir, you don't know who I am

153
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:32,280
But I have something very important that I need an answer to

154
00:11:32,280 --> 00:11:34,640
他說 哦 良聖的父子啊

155
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,920
雖然你不認識我

156
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:39,480
但是呢 我很確實的需要一個答案

157
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,160
Continuing, he said

158
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:45,360
Good teacher, I know you are a very busy man

159
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:47,160
So I will be quick

160
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:49,960
然後他也說 哎呀 父子我知道你很忙

161
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:52,040
所以我會很快的把事情說了

162
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:54,880
Doesn't that sound very much like us?

163
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:57,280
這聽起來是不是很像我們呢

164
00:11:57,280 --> 00:12:00,200
Everything we want, we want it quick

165
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:03,640
很多時候我們要一些事情我們要很快的就得到

166
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:05,560
So he cuts to the chase

167
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:07,880
所以他很快的就來到他所要說的

168
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:11,920
What must I do to have eternal life?

169
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:14,840
他說 我當做什麼才能夠承受永生呢

170
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:17,560
Oh, everyone in the crowd

171
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:21,520
They hear the question and they agree with the question

172
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:25,440
在群眾裡面呢 當然他們聽到這個問題的時候

173
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:29,040
他們也需要去知道這個答案

174
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:32,440
Everyone wants to know, but no one dares to ask

175
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:35,000
很多人都想知道 但是他們不敢去問

176
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:39,200
Even the Pharisees who have challenged Jesus earlier

177
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:43,320
are eager to hear what Jesus has to say

178
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,920
那些曾經挑戰耶穌的法利薩人

179
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:48,720
相信他們也在等著那個答案吧

180
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:53,840
People who once did not care about heaven and hell

181
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:56,480
suddenly are interested

182
00:12:56,480 --> 00:13:00,200
那些呢 從來不關懷什麼是天堂 什麼是地獄的

183
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:02,640
相信這時候他們也有興趣知道

184
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:06,120
Wow, even Jesus' own disciples

185
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:09,520
waited for their teacher's answer

186
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:13,640
我相信當時門徒們呢 也在等著耶穌的答案

187
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:15,560
It was a great question

188
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,640
這是一個很好的問題

189
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:21,120
It reminds me of the story of a married couple

190
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:25,160
這個就讓我想起有一個故事關於一個夫婦

191
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:27,520
They are both about 60 years old

192
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,480
他們兩個大概都60歲了

193
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:32,680
And they are celebrating their 35th anniversary

194
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:35,440
他們在慶祝他們35週年的紀念

195
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:37,440
And during their party

196
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,720
然後在他們的慶祝會上的時候

197
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:42,800
A genie appeared to congratulate them

198
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:46,640
and to grant them each one wish

199
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:47,960
有一個精靈出現

200
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:50,120
然後呢 就對他們夫婦說

201
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:52,720
我會給你們每一個人一個願望

202
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:55,320
The wife wanted to travel the world

203
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,920
這個妻子呢 就很想去環遊世界

204
00:13:57,920 --> 00:14:02,440
So the genie waved the wand and poof!

205
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:07,160
wife has tickets in her hand for a world cruise

206
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:09,600
然後這精靈就揮棒

207
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:13,360
然後呢 那個妻子的手中就有一張

208
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:18,440
環遊世界的輪船

209
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:21,440
Next

210
00:14:21,440 --> 00:14:24,520
The genie asked the husband what he wanted

211
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:26,760
然後這個精靈就問他的丈夫

212
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:28,760
啊 你需要什麼呢

213
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:33,520
The 60-year-old man who loves his wife said

214
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:37,640
這個很愛他妻子的60歲的老公就說

215
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:42,680
I wish I have a wife 30 years younger than me

216
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:46,080
我希望有一個比我年輕30歲的妻子

217
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:50,000
So genie picked the wand and poof!

218
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,840
然後這個精靈呢 也把棒子一揮

219
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:55,000
The husband is 90 years old

220
00:14:55,000 --> 00:15:00,440
那這個丈夫就變成90歲了

221
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:03,400
The young man had a great question

222
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:05,760
剛才那個年輕人他有一個很好的問題

223
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:08,400
The problem is we know what we want

224
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:12,160
but we often don't know what we are asking

225
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:14,800
很多時候我們知道我們要什麼

226
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:17,680
但是我們不知道自己在問什麼

227
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:22,240
What must I do? What must I accomplish

228
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:26,360
in order to acquire eternal life?

229
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:29,400
他所注重的是 我可以做什麼

230
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:32,160
才能夠承受永生

231
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:37,080
We must follow the one who is good

232
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:40,200
我們必須要跟隨那個良善的

233
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:43,840
Jesus says why do you call me good?

234
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:47,480
耶穌問他說 你為什麼稱我是良善的

235
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:53,000
Let me ask you why do you call Jesus good?

236
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,120
我要問你們 你們為什麼覺得

237
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,640
耶穌是好的 是良善的呢

238
00:15:57,640 --> 00:16:02,640
Why do you say that this whole church thing is good?

239
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:04,560
為什麼你說來到教會裡面

240
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:08,200
好多事情都是好的呢

241
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:14,200
To human beings, something is good

242
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:17,760
if it is agreeable, if it is favorable

243
00:16:17,760 --> 00:16:21,520
and if it is satisfying, it's good

244
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:23,560
對我們人來說的話呢

245
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:26,600
好的事情就是符合我們的要求

246
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:30,240
是我們希望要的 也能夠滿足我們的

247
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:33,280
First class on an airplane is good

248
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:36,720
飛機的頭等艙是好的

249
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:40,080
A+ on a test is good

250
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:43,560
考試拿到A+是好的

251
00:16:43,560 --> 00:16:48,880
Cold air on a hot day is good

252
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,680
然後在一個熱天的時候

253
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:52,720
有一陣涼風是好的

254
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:56,920
Good is invariably a positive return

255
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:59,720
that meets our approval

256
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:02,760
而這個好呢 就好像是經過我們的同意

257
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:04,800
然後有一個很好的回報

258
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:08,480
The goodness of God is His Holiness

259
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:11,280
但是神的好呢 是祂的聖潔

260
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:13,600
His perfection 祂的完美

261
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:16,640
and His sovereignty 還有祂的至高無上

262
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:22,280
Good in God is absolute excellence

263
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:25,480
好在對神來說是真的沒有什麼可比

264
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:27,800
是真的在高高之上的

265
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:31,400
Good by man standard is simply emotions

266
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:36,240
and experience that drives our ambition

267
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:38,800
人的好呢 只是因為我們的情緒

268
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,680
我們的需要 我們的目的

269
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:43,800
讓我們真的向著這個志向去追求

270
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:47,800
但是這個都是有限的

271
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:50,120
Do you know who Jesus is?

272
00:17:50,120 --> 00:17:51,920
你知道耶穌是誰嗎?

273
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:57,600
See the young man sees Jesus merely as an agent

274
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:59,520
rather the answer

275
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:02,200
我覺得這個年輕人呢 看耶穌呢

276
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,800
就是一個代言人

277
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:06,920
但是他沒有真正的注重在那個答案上面

278
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:11,400
That's because he was only interested in his own benefit

279
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:15,200
因為他所注重的是自身的那個需要

280
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:23,200
He was looking and searching to bridge his fortune on earth

281
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:31,320
while living to extend his prosperity into eternal life

282
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:33,960
He doesn't want to lose his earthly treasure

283
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:36,200
He wants to build on

284
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:40,200
so that he can bring it with him to eternal life

285
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:44,560
他其實就是想保住他現在在世的這些財富

286
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:46,360
然後要有一個保障

287
00:18:46,360 --> 00:18:53,000
能把這些財富繼續的在他死亡之後能難的存在

288
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:58,400
Let that not be our mistake

289
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:01,720
Only God is truly good

290
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:04,040
and because he is good

291
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:06,600
he knows what's best for us

292
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:09,920
因為只有神是那位良善那位好的

293
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:13,240
而且他很清楚的知道什麼對我們是最好的

294
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:18,320
We must follow the one who is good

295
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:24,640
And two, we must follow the one who is righteous

296
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:30,080
Eternal life is not something anyone can do to earn

297
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:33,040
永生不是我們可以去賺取的

298
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:37,080
But our earthly training when we go to school, when we go to work

299
00:19:37,080 --> 00:19:39,880
it tells us that there is a cause

300
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:43,920
and there is an effect in how this world operates

301
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:47,000
但是當我們去上學或者去上班的時候

302
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:50,320
這個世界的一個定論就是告訴我們

303
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,880
你做的什麼你就會得到什麼

304
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:55,200
You do this, you get that

305
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:57,520
你做這個,你就得到那個

306
00:19:57,520 --> 00:20:00,520
But no amount of things that we do

307
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:04,160
equate to the sacrifice of our Lord Jesus Christ

308
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,000
但是無論我們做什麼呢

309
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:08,440
都不能夠跟耶穌的犧牲相等

310
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:11,080
It is only through the shedding of his blood

311
00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:13,240
and the breaking of his body

312
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:18,120
can we as sinners be reconciled to God

313
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:21,960
接著耶穌的保血和他破碎的身體呢

314
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:23,920
我們才能夠與神和好

315
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:30,320
Salvation is not acquired by any means or any effort

316
00:20:30,320 --> 00:20:34,480
真的,救恩不能夠通過我們做的一些事情

317
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:36,520
或者是去行的一些事情所得到

318
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:42,080
It must begin with obedience to the one who is righteous

319
00:20:42,080 --> 00:20:45,800
而是必須向那位公義的信號順服

320
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:48,400
And it is interesting that Jesus answered

321
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:52,640
with something that the young man was very familiar with

322
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,320
而且我們也覺得很奇怪

323
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:57,320
耶穌用了這個年輕人所知道的

324
00:20:57,320 --> 00:21:00,960
一些的問題來回答他

325
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:06,200
Jesus quoted the second half of the Ten Commandments

326
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:09,960
耶穌用了十誡中的後五誡來回答他

327
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:13,640
Don't commit adultery, do not kill, do not murder

328
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:17,960
Do not steal, do not bear false witness, do not cheat

329
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:23,840
But honor your mother and honor your father

330
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:27,240
他告訴他不可殺人,不可奸淫

331
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:30,160
不可偷盜,不可做假見證

332
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:34,080
不可恢復人,但是當孝敬父母

333
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,680
You know what I thought was interesting

334
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,400
When Jesus was with the children

335
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:40,080
He did not tell the children any of this

336
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:45,960
But he tells the young man, us brothers and sisters

337
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:48,240
Second half of the Ten Commandments

338
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:50,880
And honor your mother and father

339
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:54,160
我很奇怪,就是耶穌在跟孩子在一起的時候

340
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,960
他並沒有告訴他們這些

341
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:58,760
但是他告訴年輕人這些

342
00:21:58,760 --> 00:22:02,120
而且特別注重在要孝敬父母

343
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:04,000
The first five Ten Commandments

344
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:06,840
pertain to our relationship with God

345
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:10,080
實際的前五階呢是我們跟神的關係

346
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:14,440
The second half has to do with our relationship with other people

347
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:18,040
但是後五階呢確實告訴我們我們與人的關係

348
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:21,920
You see the young man was a ruler of people

349
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:24,920
我們知道這個年輕人是一個領導

350
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:27,760
He is an authority over people

351
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:29,400
他也是去管理人的

352
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:32,240
He is a representative of people

353
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,920
他也是代表人民的

354
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,640
And this is his reply

355
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:37,320
這個就是他的回答

356
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:42,760
Teacher, all these I have observed from my youth

357
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:45,040
I have been a good boy

358
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:46,640
他跟他耶穌說

359
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:49,160
夫子這一切我從小就做了

360
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,120
都遵守了

361
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,720
I have complied

362
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,000
我已經做完了

363
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,360
I have not been bad

364
00:22:54,360 --> 00:22:56,240
我沒有做壞事

365
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,440
I have been very good

366
00:22:58,440 --> 00:23:00,160
我是一個很好的人

367
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:09,760
Parents, it is wonderful to teach our children to be good

368
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:10,320
很好

369
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:13,840
如果你教你的孩子去做好的是很好的事情

370
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:17,200
It is awesome to want our children to behave

371
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,240
to work hard

372
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:18,880
to study

373
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:20,840
to do all the things well

374
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:23,080
要我們的孩子有一個好的表現

375
00:23:23,080 --> 00:23:24,120
去努力

376
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:26,120
去做一些很好的事情

377
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:28,600
一切都是很好很美好的

378
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:34,240
But being good is only half the prize

379
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:37,840
但是做好的就是只是一半的獎賞

380
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:41,120
The other half is truth

381
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:43,560
但是另一半就是要去懂得真理

382
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:47,400
Do we teach our children the truth?

383
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:50,120
我們有沒有教導孩子真理

384
00:23:50,120 --> 00:23:53,440
Good is by having confidence in self

385
00:23:53,440 --> 00:23:56,200
好是因為我們對自己有自信

386
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:59,200
Truth is having faith in Christ

387
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:02,080
但是真理就是我們對神有信心

388
00:24:02,080 --> 00:24:05,240
Knowing Jesus is only half the joy

389
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:08,160
我們認識神只是一半的喜樂

390
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:12,680
But doing His will completes your blessing

391
00:24:12,680 --> 00:24:16,280
但是我們如果能夠去遵守他給我們的旨意

392
00:24:16,280 --> 00:24:17,880
我們就把一切都完成了

393
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:20,040
You know what Jesus gave him?

394
00:24:20,040 --> 00:24:22,200
你知道耶穌給他什麼嗎

395
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:24,920
Jesus looked at him

396
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:28,280
and he gave the man what he was missing

397
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:33,080
他就給這個年輕人所錯失的

398
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:35,880
Jesus loved him

399
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,840
耶穌愛他

400
00:24:37,840 --> 00:24:41,560
The story of the rich young man

401
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:43,560
as I said earlier

402
00:24:43,560 --> 00:24:47,920
appears in three of the four gospel books

403
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:50,320
我們知道這個年輕人的故事

404
00:24:50,320 --> 00:24:53,200
在世福音當中有三個福音在記載

405
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:57,520
But only in Mark was it noted

406
00:24:57,520 --> 00:25:00,000
that Jesus looked at him

407
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:02,400
at the young man and loved him

408
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:04,280
但只是在馬可福音裡面

409
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:07,000
我們可以看到耶穌寫著

410
00:25:07,000 --> 00:25:08,400
這個書裡面寫著

411
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:10,680
耶穌看著他就愛他

412
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:13,320
Mark couldn't have been the better person

413
00:25:13,320 --> 00:25:17,480
to write such a profound caption about Jesus

414
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:22,000
馬可真的是寫這個句子的最好人選

415
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:25,800
See Mark was not one of the twelve disciples

416
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:29,000
因為我們知道馬可不是十二門徒裡面的一位

417
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:33,240
In fact his faith was in and out, up and down

418
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:37,200
我們知道他的信心也是上上下下起起伏伏的

419
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:42,960
But to be so moved upon seeing the true character of Jesus

420
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:47,280
it was important that Mark wrote this down

421
00:25:47,280 --> 00:25:51,720
但是當他在那邊看到神的真心情的時候呢

422
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:55,440
他真的要把這個動作寫下來

423
00:25:55,440 --> 00:26:00,160
And he thought it was important that others might read it

424
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:03,400
and know the love of Jesus Christ

425
00:26:03,400 --> 00:26:05,680
而且他也覺得這是很重要的

426
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:07,320
把這一個記錄下來

427
00:26:07,320 --> 00:26:09,720
讓別人也能夠看到耶穌的愛

428
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:13,240
In our relationship with brothers and sisters

429
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:15,600
我們與弟兄姊妹之間的關係

430
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:20,560
We must be more Christ-like in the way we love one another

431
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:22,160
當我們彼此相愛的時候

432
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:23,840
我們真的要特別的學上

433
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:28,680
How Jesus can just love people with such pure conviction

434
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:30,680
such deep compassion

435
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:33,480
and with such authentic affection

436
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:36,720
is something we all must learn

437
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:40,320
我們真的看到耶穌真的是很純粹的去愛人

438
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:44,200
而且他有很深的側眼的心去愛別人

439
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:48,520
We are sinners

440
00:26:48,520 --> 00:26:49,840
我們都是罪人

441
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:54,120
We are broken people

442
00:26:54,120 --> 00:27:00,040
But in Christ His love covers all of our shortcomings

443
00:27:00,040 --> 00:27:01,840
但是在基督裡面呢

444
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:04,880
他的愛把我們的一切缺點都遮蓋了

445
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:10,120
We are to share the love that we have received from our Lord

446
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:14,160
我們真的要去分享我們從神得來的愛

447
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:18,480
Last month our youth helped raise funds

448
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:21,760
for the Thailand missions

449
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:27,080
上個月我們的年輕人他們為泰國的事情來籌款

450
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:32,480
Last week our children assembled 155 boxes

451
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:34,640
to share with other children

452
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:39,840
上個星期我們的兒童們也裝了155個鞋盒

453
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,960
去與其他的小孩子分享

454
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:47,320
Our church is getting ready to support the missions in Bangladesh

455
00:27:47,320 --> 00:27:52,320
而且我們教會也在準備去支持孟加拉的一些的宣教

456
00:27:52,320 --> 00:27:53,880
Maybe even Japan

457
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:55,640
或者更遠的是日本

458
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:57,720
We share as a church

459
00:27:57,720 --> 00:28:02,840
because others have given so we may also have

460
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:06,120
因為我們去分享是因為別人所給我們

461
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:08,160
我們也能夠去分享給別人

462
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:12,600
We love because Christ loved us first

463
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:15,480
我們去愛也是因為神先愛我們

464
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:18,360
We must follow the one who is life

465
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:20,840
我們也必須跟隨那是生命的

466
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:23,640
Jesus knows where the young man has been

467
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:26,040
and where the young man is heading

468
00:28:26,040 --> 00:28:29,040
耶穌知道這個年輕人是從哪裡來的

469
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:31,400
他現在也是在這往哪裡去

470
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:33,000
So like a good doctor

471
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:37,080
Jesus gave him the young man's prognosis

472
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:39,280
而成為一個好的醫生

473
00:28:39,280 --> 00:28:42,240
他也給這個年輕人一個診斷

474
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:45,640
One thing you lack in life

475
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,000
你還缺少一件

476
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:54,560
And Jesus tells him three things that he must first do

477
00:28:54,560 --> 00:28:59,200
而且耶穌也告訴他有三樣事情他必須先做

478
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:04,960
Go, sell and give

479
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:09,360
你要去賣然後要去給

480
00:29:09,360 --> 00:29:10,800
Why go?

481
00:29:10,800 --> 00:29:12,480
為什麼要去呢

482
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:17,800
Because when we go we look back at our traveled past

483
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:19,160
因為當我們去的時候

484
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:22,080
我們看到我們以前所發生的一些事情

485
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:26,160
It is a chance that Jesus is giving us

486
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:28,800
to change and to repent

487
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:31,680
這個是耶穌給我們一個去改變

488
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,160
去悔改的機會

489
00:29:33,160 --> 00:29:34,960
Why sell?

490
00:29:34,960 --> 00:29:38,200
你為什麼要去變賣呢

491
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:46,840
To permanently let go of the things that control us

492
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:49,320
Why give?

493
00:29:49,320 --> 00:29:56,280
To share with others what God has blessed us

494
00:29:56,280 --> 00:30:01,720
But see, many people see this as a problem

495
00:30:01,720 --> 00:30:06,040
We see ourselves as fish in water

496
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:09,200
and the water is being taken away from us

497
00:30:09,200 --> 00:30:12,240
我們會感覺到我們是在水中的魚

498
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:14,640
但是我們的水被別人拿走了

499
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:18,960
But actually we are like fish being set free from the bowl

500
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:22,440
into the ocean of endless opportunities

501
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:27,200
但是其實我們就是一隻被放進大海的一隻魚

502
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:29,480
而且有很多很多的機會

503
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:33,400
And Jesus didn't just say give everything away

504
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:37,040
耶穌也不單只是說把一切都給出去吧

505
00:30:37,040 --> 00:30:40,640
Instead, Jesus tells him to give to the poor

506
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:43,640
而且耶穌叫他要去給窮人

507
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:47,880
Even though material possessions mean nothing to God

508
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:51,640
雖然物質的事情對神來說是沒有什麼意義的

509
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,960
Our God is not a wasteful God

510
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:56,320
但是祂也不是一個浪費的耶穌

511
00:30:56,320 --> 00:30:58,560
He is the way, the truth, and the life

512
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:01,280
祂是真理,道路,生命

513
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:03,480
最後一點

514
00:31:03,480 --> 00:31:06,680
We must follow the one who is Lord

515
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:09,200
我們必須跟隨那位是主的

516
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:12,040
Finally, Jesus said this to him

517
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:15,120
最後呢,耶穌跟他說

518
00:31:15,120 --> 00:31:18,920
And then you come and follow me

519
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:21,520
你還要來跟從我

520
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:24,960
Now, it is not mentioned in this passage

521
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:28,160
But I am sure brothers and sisters are very familiar

522
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:31,880
That when Jesus usually say come and follow me

523
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:34,160
It involves taking up your cross

524
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:36,680
雖然在這個經文裡面沒有記載

525
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,880
但是很多時候當我們聽到耶穌說

526
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:40,680
來跟從我的時候呢

527
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,880
通常都會跟著要背棄你的屍駕

528
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:46,560
It is commonly known as the cost of discipleship

529
00:31:46,560 --> 00:31:51,840
而且呢這個就是好像一個作為信徒的一個要做的事情

530
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:55,760
I think it is more of a reward than a cost

531
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:59,240
但是呢我覺得這個對我們來說其實是一個獎賞

532
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,560
而不是一個代價

533
00:32:00,560 --> 00:32:06,200
Following Jesus only means that God is going to be with you everywhere you go

534
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:09,840
而且呢這個代表著無論我們到哪裡去

535
00:32:09,840 --> 00:32:11,480
神都會跟我們同在

536
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:14,080
But we must accept His invitation

537
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:19,040
但是我們首先要接受祂的邀請

538
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:22,640
We must be willing to take up our own cross

539
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:25,160
我們必須背棄我們自己的屍駕

540
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:29,080
We must deny our self

541
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:33,600
Put our old self behind

542
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:36,560
and follow Him

543
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:39,840
The Bible doesn't tell us what happened to the young man

544
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:43,120
聖經沒有告訴我們後來這個年輕人怎麼樣了

545
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:47,480
But he was sad

546
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:51,680
He walked away sorrowfully

547
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:56,320
because he had great possessions

548
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:58,680
He was a good man

549
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:02,000
He kept all the laws

550
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:05,280
He honored his parents

551
00:33:05,280 --> 00:33:08,760
He made a good living

552
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:14,640
He even came face to face with Jesus Christ the superstar

553
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:18,080
而且呢他也跟耶穌面對面了

554
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:22,440
But that fish stayed in its bowl

555
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:26,560
但是這隻魚呢卻在他的魚缸裡面

556
00:33:26,560 --> 00:33:29,840
His wealth, his fame, his treasures

557
00:33:29,840 --> 00:33:32,120
They were his master

558
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:36,640
他的財產,他的名聲都成為了他的主人

559
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:40,120
We must follow the one who is good and righteous

560
00:33:40,120 --> 00:33:43,640
我們必須跟隨那個良善,那個公義的

561
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:47,160
We must follow the one who is love and life

562
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:50,240
我們也必須跟隨那個有愛,有生命的

563
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:53,360
We must follow the one who is Lord

564
00:33:53,360 --> 00:33:56,440
而且我們也必須跟隨那個主

565
00:33:56,440 --> 00:34:00,400
Don't just come when you need something

566
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:03,520
不要只是單單你需要什麼的時候才來

567
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:07,560
Jesus says come and follow me

568
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:10,800
耶穌跟他說你來跟從我

569
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:16,200
Don't just come to take care whatever you need to take care of

570
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:19,640
不要只是來來解決你一切的需要

571
00:34:19,640 --> 00:34:25,280
Jesus says take up your cross, then come and follow me

572
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:28,800
耶穌說背起你的支架,來跟從我

573
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:33,760
Let me conclude by sharing a prayer by someone

574
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:37,480
after reading the story of the rich young man

575
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:40,480
我要分享一個就是一個人

576
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:43,760
他看完這個年輕人的故事之後

577
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:44,880
一個的禱告

578
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:48,960
So this is this man's prayer after reading this story

579
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:51,040
所以這個是這個人的一個禱告

580
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:53,680
當他唸完這個經文之後

581
00:34:53,680 --> 00:34:57,200
He says dear Lord

582
00:34:57,200 --> 00:35:02,040
I've been reading and rereading the record of the rich young ruler

583
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:05,120
and his obvious wrong choices

584
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:08,760
我持續的在唸這一段的經文

585
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:12,400
然後我就看到這個年輕人的一些錯誤的選擇

586
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:15,000
But it has set me thinking Lord

587
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:18,520
但是呢這就讓我再一次的去思考

588
00:35:18,520 --> 00:35:22,600
No matter how much wealth this young man had

589
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:26,440
不論這個年輕人是多麼的富有

590
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:30,000
He could not ride in a car

591
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:34,040
當時的他不能夠去駕著一輛車

592
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:38,440
Remember this is a story from 2000 plus years ago

593
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:42,080
因為這個故事是記載在2000多年前了

594
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:46,040
And he cannot have surgery when he wants to

595
00:35:46,040 --> 00:35:47,200
or when he needs to

596
00:35:47,200 --> 00:35:49,520
當他有生病或者什麼事情的時候

597
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:51,640
他也不能夠去做手術

598
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:54,000
He cannot turn on the light

599
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:56,000
他也不能夠去打開電燈

600
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,480
There's no electricity then

601
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:59,120
因為那時候並沒有電

602
00:35:59,120 --> 00:36:04,600
He cannot buy important medicine like penicillin

603
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:06,360
He cannot buy penicillin

604
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:09,600
他也不能夠去買那些很重要的藥物

605
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:10,840
比如盤尼斯林

606
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:14,320
He cannot hear the grand piano

607
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:16,520
他也聽不到鋼琴的聲音

608
00:36:16,520 --> 00:36:17,920
He cannot watch TV

609
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,440
也看不到電視

610
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:22,680
He cannot wash dishes in running water

611
00:36:22,680 --> 00:36:25,440
他也不能夠用自來水去洗碗

612
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:28,560
He cannot type a letter or send an email

613
00:36:28,560 --> 00:36:32,160
他也不能夠去發電郵或者是去打一封信

614
00:36:32,160 --> 00:36:33,880
He cannot mow the lawn

615
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:36,360
他也不能夠去用除草機去除草

616
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:38,280
He cannot fly in an airplane

617
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:40,720
他也不能夠去駕一輛飛機

618
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:43,720
He cannot sleep on an innerspring mattress

619
00:36:43,720 --> 00:36:45,720
他也不能夠睡在彈簧床上

620
00:36:45,720 --> 00:36:48,760
He cannot even go on the internet or talk on the phone

621
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:51,360
他也不能夠上網或者是通電話

622
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:56,640
So Lord, if this young man was rich

623
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:59,200
如果這個年輕人是這麼的富有

624
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:01,360
Then what am I?

625
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:04,560
那我又怎麼樣呢?

626
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:07,040
What I think he is saying is

627
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:11,760
我想他是這樣講的

628
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:15,080
We can have anything and we can have everything

629
00:37:15,080 --> 00:37:18,120
But if we do not have the Lord

630
00:37:18,120 --> 00:37:23,600
No matter how rich or loaded you are

631
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:25,000
You have nothing

632
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:28,160
因為無論我們是多麼的富有

633
00:37:28,160 --> 00:37:30,040
我們擁有什麼的東西

634
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:32,560
很多很多的物件

635
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:34,440
但是呢如果我們沒有神

636
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,960
我們什麼都不是

637
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:40,760
So when you say grace at the dinner table this Thanksgiving

638
00:37:40,760 --> 00:37:46,800
所以當今年你在感恩桌上做這個禱告的時候

639
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:50,760
Remember everything is the Lord's provision

640
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:53,760
要記得這一切都是從神而來的

641
00:37:53,760 --> 00:37:56,040
And after the dishes are done

642
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:58,800
Yes, don't forget you still have to do dishes

643
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:03,360
而且呢吃完飯之後要把碗洗了

644
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:06,360
And your children or your family go to bed

645
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:09,280
那你的孩子要去睡覺了

646
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,960
Ask yourself this question

647
00:38:10,960 --> 00:38:13,600
你要問自己這個問題

648
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:15,360
Who am I following?

649
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:17,520
你跟從誰?

650
00:38:17,520 --> 00:38:19,200
Who am I following?

651
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:20,960
你跟從誰呢?

652
00:38:20,960 --> 00:38:23,120
May the peace of the Lord be with all of you

653
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,080
願神的祝福與你們同在

654
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:26,080
Amen

